" Simplify movement around windows               {{{2
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

" Simplify changing window arrangement           {{{2
nnoremap <C-S-h> <C-w>H
nnoremap <C-S-j> <C-w>J
nnoremap <C-S-k> <C-w>K
nnoremap <C-S-l> <C-w>L

" Simplify movement around soft-wrapped lines    {{{2
nnoremap ¶ gj
nnoremap § gk
